Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下跪的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有向御子乃傳達到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！我的洞…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往希望的道路沒有了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質的原子排列
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連一點破綻都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被埋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅僅是被埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還注入了Element能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把洞給填住了的犯人就在牆壁的那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在女學生之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女學生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是擁有怎樣心境的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個洞填住的可愛女學生正渴求著被誰貫穿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的魔鬼身材的女學生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填住這個的可能是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本就沒有考慮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這支曲子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是修雷特在彈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個聖天使學院的第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Element的特招生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訓練也被免除了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很少出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從秘密情報那裡得知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的照片在女生之間 銷量排名第一哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你去哪裡啊 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 修雷特 不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的模擬戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模擬器奏響了有趣的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:05:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你發出的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然能知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是非常直率而特別的音色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音色就算不會言語
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它卻能夠傳達人的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至能夠撼動人的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我叫阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特·艾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇啊 摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是來找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模擬戰裡的那個醜樣是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我把你砍掉重練嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能不要在這個房間起爭執呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對魔星最不拿手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你不要亂動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修 修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.26,0:07:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺出一副酷酷的面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出的事可真是陰險啊 修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特的Element能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家伙可以用音樂來影響人的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你內心的根源搖蕩得相當厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫御子乃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在擔心妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真敢做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先挑釁的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不和諧的音符 很接近了
