Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}重複一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔 到我們出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}出擊的Element是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}怪炎 安迪 阿馬塔 三人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vector X 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Y 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Z 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的不是訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是真正的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是難以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然連續兩次把新人投入實戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion的力量還是未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種可以將這種力量引發出來的素質
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後的敵人有著繼續強化的征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何一個能通向勝利的法則
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要盡量掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是人型的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前一樣的雜魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們大鬧一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion M
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion在戰鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道還有阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近 有種令人討厭的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強 明明對方是無人機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種有組織的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟以往的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某處 有著指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到本體不明的show time了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去就遭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了改變Element
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓王牌的修雷特去之外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有其他的辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制著這些家伙的老大在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我將你的力量覺醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被纏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然動不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴的琴音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特 你想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這畫面是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 真遺憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人在命運三星的上方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 就算想把他打下來也夠不著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抓住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在靠岸太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船在往回開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運被轉動了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:14:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的吧 一次都沒有和女生合體就被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪的精神等級低下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話 合體無法維持了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學院長 啊不對司令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求Element替換
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請全員替換
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請只讓我們女生戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 請下決定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學院長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Element替換
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪·W·霍爾 強制召回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替換為御子乃·鈴白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不需要局外人來指使
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼啊 這像小丑一樣的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動·ZEN
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等您許久了 不動總司令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總 總司令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃·鈴白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去乘坐Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 我不可能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能成為Element
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些冒失的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠保護重要的人的手段只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 只有傷害自己這一種手段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說沒用的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快離開那男人 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃 別磨磨蹭蹭的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 一直都是被保護的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪炎和阿馬塔君代替著我承受傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:16:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起內心痛苦要好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我也是被保護著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 已經到達極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合體被解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都做不到的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實我什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想再一次握緊雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這股氣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Element替換
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔君 合體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 然後我就原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼喊吧 阿馬塔·空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融雪合體 GO Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Evol
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和神樂戰鬥的形態呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體規格已經調查完畢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃 為什麼登上了Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…只有你 我不想送上戰場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:17:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小時候開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便不斷重複的絕望的預知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來向我宣告的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你接近了Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨後就會喪命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 想要保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被你憎恨著 也要把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直被這手保護著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到現在 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我已經厭倦了只被人保護著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想保護怪炎 我的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我也想被傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔君也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以再做那種事情了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢 和御子乃在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…總感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion和Element的聯動數值不斷上升
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion在心動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion的胸腔不停息的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這便是青春的鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了 心跳不止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種呼之欲出的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手牽手 心連心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高漲的鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達至蒼穹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion的手臂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說之技 無限拳現在復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又一個封印被解開了呢 不動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到還會有這樣不得了的技能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取得了這樣的數據的話 出雲也沒有怨言了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拳骨到底能延伸到何處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 朝我們Neo Diva本部來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏…柏林牆被…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分割男女的牆壁被毀壞的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.00,0:22:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在對你們宣告
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了嗎 禁止戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.92,0:01:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============ed=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.95,0:22:49.26,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}風に奪われたわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.40,0:22:52.08,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}片道分の勇気で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.24,0:22:59.73,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}僕ら 悲劇を受け入れる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:04.47,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}心がここにあったはずの空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:07.39,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}もっと僕が大きければ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.48,0:23:13.08,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}君を未来を救えただろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:17.51,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}大切な人を　守る術が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.66,0:23:20.44,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}たった一つが持てない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:23.11,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そんな あなたが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:26.70,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}はぐれ漂う空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:34.51,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}あなた以上の 人に出逢えない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.75,0:23:40.60,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}月に抗う長いフレア
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.22,0:23:47.62,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}始まりもせず終わる物語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:51.65,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}傷つきうる 柔らかさ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.84,0:23:54.04,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}閉じ込めた旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.06,0:24:01.08,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}奏でるほど 歌うほど 壊れるほどに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.47,0:24:08.75,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}あなたが恋しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.95,0:22:49.26,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}並不是被風奪去了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.40,0:22:52.08,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}憑借著單程份的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.24,0:22:59.73,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我們接受著並且接納著悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:04.47,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}應該存在心靈的空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:07.39,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}如果我能夠更加強大的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.48,0:23:13.08,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}是否能夠拯救你 拯救未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:17.51,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}能夠守護重要的人的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.66,0:23:20.44,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:23.11,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}就算是這樣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:26.70,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}在這零散漂泊的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:34.51,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}再也不會擁有如此美妙的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.75,0:23:40.60,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}漫長歲月抵抗著月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.22,0:23:47.62,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}還沒有開始就結束了的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:51.65,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}通過傷害得到的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.84,0:23:54.04,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}被束縛的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.06,0:24:01.08,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}越發演奏 越發歌唱 就如同壞掉般
